</h2>
<div class="grid">
<section class="main col-full">
<h3>This Privacy Policy applies to our sites and apps</h3>
<p>
Ebert Digital LLC&rsquo;s &ldquo;hereinafter Ebert Digital&rdquo; Privacy Policy is designed to inform users about the type of information we collect, and how we collect, use and safeguard the information we collect on our Website. By using our website and app, you consent to our Privacy Policy.
</p>
<p class="italic">This policy was last updated on May 28, 2013.</p>
